               <p>Before Mr. Recorder.</p>
               <p>1187. 
               
                  <persName id="t18230910-218-defend1996" type="defendantName">
                     CHARLOTTE 
                     THOMAS
                  <interp inst="t18230910-218-defend1996" type="surname" value="THOMAS"></interp>
